{"tid":2335194,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"仲有三日就到聖誕","createTime":"2020-12-21T16:14:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-21T17:31:38.000Z","uid":370062,"like":5,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"26b83fb06d20daaade631b9e6d04f87273ac4f2e","tid":2335194,"uid":370062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T16:14:18.000Z","msg":"希望各位連登巴絲可以開開心心過聖誕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無論親情友情定愛情都可以一直保持落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n聖誕當日約咗屋企人朋友另一半嘅玩得開心啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n未約嘅希望你哋快啲約到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n溝緊仔或女嘅希望你哋快啲溝到然後甜甜蜜蜜過聖誕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n總之希望大家今年過個開心愉快幸福嘅聖誕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好好似本行咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b73b514e67a51894b5133e887bc71550f7bf1203","tid":2335194,"uid":305269,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T16:14:41.000Z","msg":"本行on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58836473f8712a48d09cf0979e25ca170c956bcd","tid":2335194,"uid":370062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b73b514e67a51894b5133e887bc71550f7bf1203","tid":2335194,"uid":305269,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T16:14:41.000Z","msg":"本行on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T16:15:09.000Z","msg":"行非on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1332b5d9c1251ca2b1c8d009ff5ae705b21642a4","tid":2335194,"uid":236650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T16:20:03.000Z","msg":"究竟開咗幾多個同類嘅post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2c0a258670385fe608053f3ff3582901d0b5128","tid":2335194,"uid"